64
00:06:12,822 --> 00:06:14,942
- Ugh! Not that.
- Oh?

65
00:06:15,024 --> 00:06:19,034
Is it true, Phaka?
I heard the rumors all over the market.

66
00:06:19,197 --> 00:06:24,052
Ugh! That Phaad is so evil! He's evil,
and his gang is evil too.

67
00:06:24,108 --> 00:06:27,493
There's no way he'd suddenly
become a good person.

68
00:06:27,787 --> 00:06:30,909
Yeah, Phaad really cares about his guys.

69
00:06:31,066 --> 00:06:35,357
Last time, he and his gang beat up Loy
until he was covered in blood.

70
00:06:35,533 --> 00:06:38,648
So how could he beat up his own guys this time?

71
00:06:41,795 --> 00:06:46,588
I think that's probably because
Phaad's always had a grudge against Loy.

72
00:06:47,082 --> 00:06:51,574
Everyone knows Phaad really likes Whan.

73
00:06:52,382 --> 00:06:55,315
