I'm just saying what happened. It's nothing.

82
00:07:22,904 --> 00:07:27,658
Hey, what's wrong with you?
You're acting all nervous and weird.

83
00:07:28,322 --> 00:07:31,481
Uh... well...
I'm not feeling so good.

84
00:07:33,302 --> 00:07:36,280
Oh, you're probably still freaked out
from what happened yesterday.

85
00:07:36,687 --> 00:07:40,474
Go, go rest upstairs.
You live alone.

86
00:07:40,475 --> 00:07:43,612
We'll go get you some medicine.

87
00:07:43,838 --> 00:07:45,846
- Let's go.
- Oh! No, don't!

88
00:07:45,847 --> 00:07:50,188
